<h1 align="center">Nordic Treebank Network.<br>
	Representation formats</h1>


<a name="Purpose"></a>
<h2>Purpose</h2>

	<p>The purpose of this page is to document the representation
	formats used in the treebank projects of the Nordic Treebank
	Network, and to propose candidates for common representation
	formats, so that data can be imported/exported by the different
	tools used in the NTN.</p>

